  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Water is a vital and scarce resource all over the world, however, Fiji is made up of over 400 Islands surrounded by water but a number of Islands and communities still have no access or limited access to clean drinking water. This project implements and enhances rainwater harvesting and sanitation facilities, capacity and infrastructure, whilst ensuring the best basic hygiene and sanitation practices. Be part of the solution!</narrative>
